    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just hard to see it that way when i'm the one struggling to even walk to the kitchen alone. they have to stop everything they're doing just to help me. i hate seeing that look on their faces when they're exhausted from cleaning up after me or driving me to appointments. it feels so selfish for me to keep taking and taking when i've got nothing left to give.",
